The '''Cave Carrot''' is found via [[foraging]] in [[The Mines]].  It can also be found in [[Garbage Can]]s. Large quantities can be easily obtained by digging underground patches of dirt in [[The Mines]] (on levels 10-20) with the [[Hoes|Hoe]]. It may also randomly be found in the [[Traveling Cart]] stock for {{tprice|25}}.

