==Tailoring==
Cave Carrot is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{name|Shirt011|link=Tailoring{{!}}Green Belted Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a brown dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the orange dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*The Cave Carrot may be randomly requested during any [[Seasons|season]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|75}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.
*One, two, or five Cave Carrots may be requested by several fish in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].
*After reaching 3 [[friendship]] hearts with [[Marnie]], she will request that you bring her a Cave Carrot in the [[Quests#Marnie's Request|"Marnie's Request" quest]].  The reward is 100 [[friendship]] points with [[Marnie]].

